fig = plt.figure()
ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d')

# Make data
x = np.linspace(-4,4, 100)
y = np.linspace(-4,4, 100)
X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y)
Z = X**2 - Y**2

# Plot the surface
ax.plot_surface(X, Y, Z, color='b')
